  "texts": [
    "Research ObjectivesTo develop a glioma detection model for Segmentation and classification of 3D MRI.",
    "Reduce inspection time & manual error in diagnosis using the AI Attention mechanism.",
    "Optimize the system for real-time usage and increase accuracy.",
    "Research ChallengesThe project major challenge is designing glioma detector from 3D MRI's, a deep learning model particularly made for glioma segmentation and grading.",
    "The working of the proposed system will be evaluated with the helping metrics such as segmentation accuracy, Dice similarity coefficient, grading accuracy etc., which is supposed to be more."
